The paper discusses the design of algorithms for personalized item recommendation, which is a central topic in information retrieval (cs.IR) and machine learning (cs.LG). The focus is on deep learning (neural) techniques, which are a subset of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and deep learning (cs.DL). The paper also discusses issues in research practice, which could fall under the category of social and information sciences (cs.SI).
